[SN]TITLE[SN]
Lorry crash shuts A44 Aberystwyth and Ponterwyd road

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
The A44 in Ceredigion has been reopened after being closed to allow the recovery of a lorry which left the carriageway.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The incident happened on the road between Aberystwyth and Ponterwyd on Friday.
The A44 was closed until Saturday between the A4159 at Lovesgrove roundabout, Capel Bangor, and the A4120 at Ponterwyd.
